Le [[Aide:GreffonWiki|greffon]] **~HistoriqueAuteur** (//~AuthorHistory//) vous permet d'afficher l'historique des éditions d'un auteur particulier.
Vous pouvez également spécifier le nom de la page (page courante par défaut).

== Usage ==
{{{
<<AuthorHistory arguments>>
}}}

== Arguments ==

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Valeur par défaut
|-
| **exclude**
| Comma-separated list of pages to exclude
| none
|-
| **noheader**
| Do not display page header
| false
|-
| **includeminor**
| Include minor modifications
| false
|-
| **includedeleted**
| Include deleted pages
| false
|-
| **author**
| Display modification by this author
| Current user
|-
| **page**
| Give a page name or "all" (list all pages with edits by this user)
| Current page
|-
| **info**
| Info to display in the table
| version, minor, author, summary, mtime
|}

== Examples ==

{{{
<<AuthorHistory page=HomePage includeminor=1>>
}}}

{{{
<<AuthorHistory page=all>>
}}}

